OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784922490
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist whose data was
OL,4,Cunlawfully gained awarded #20,000 in
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FA former BBC journalist whose
OL,8,Fcommunications data was unlawfully
OL,9,Fobtained by MI5 has been awarded
OL,10,F#20,000 in damages by a specialist
OL,11,Ftribunal.
OL,13,FThe Security Service previously
OL,14,Fadmitted it breached the rights of
OL,15,FVincent Kearney, now the northern
OL,16,Feditor at RTE, when obtaining the data.
OL,26,@xD@Mrb
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
