PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784922490
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist whose data was
OL,4,Cunlawfully gained awarded #20,000 in
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,8,F(PSNI) and Metropolitan Police also
OL,9,Fmade concessions during proceedings
OL,10,Fbrought by Mr Kearney at the
OL,11,FInvestigatory Powers Tribunal (IPT).
OL,13,FIn a judgment on Thursday, three
OL,14,Fjudges at the IPT awarded Mr Kearney
OL,15,F#10,000 in damages from the PSNI and
OL,16,Fthe same award against MI5, finding
OL,17,Fthere was "no reason to distinguish
OL,18,Fbetween the conduct" of the two
OL,19,Forganisations.
OL,26,@yD@KOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784922490
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist whose data was
OL,4,Cunlawfully gained awarded #20,000 in
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FLady Carmichael, Mr Justice
OL,8,FChamberlain and Stephen Shaw KC said
OL,9,Fthat "the interferences in this case
OL,10,Fwere numerous, and took place over a
OL,11,Fperiod of years".
OL,13,FThe judges continued: "The heightened
OL,14,Fprotection provided to journalists is
OL,15,Fnot for the benefit of the journalist
OL,16,Fpersonally, but for the public
OL,17,Finterest in the ability of his readers
OL,18,For audience to receive information
OL,19,Ffrom him."
OL,26,@qD@FOUsD@PO]uD@WOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
