PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784922490
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist whose data was
OL,4,Cunlawfully gained awarded #20,000 in
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FMr Kearney brought legal action after
OL,8,Freports that documents in the case of
OL,9,Fdocumentary makers Barry McCaffrey and
OL,10,FTrevor Birney had suggested that
OL,11,Fpublic bodies, including police
OL,12,Fforces, had spied on Mr Kearney.
OL,14,FAt a hearing in February, Jude Bunting
OL,15,FKC, for Mr Kearney and the BBC, said
OL,16,Fthere were seven separate police or
OL,17,FMI5 operations where the intelligence
OL,18,Fservices or forces unlawfully obtained
OL,19,Fthe journalist's or broadcaster's
OL,20,Fconfidential communications data
OL,21,Fbetween 2006 and 2018.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784922490
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist whose data was
OL,4,Cunlawfully gained awarded #20,000 in
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FThe tribunal in London was told that
OL,8,Fthe PSNI had made a "detailed profile"
OL,9,Fof the journalist, including his date
OL,10,Fof birth, addresses, car details,
OL,11,Fphone numbers and the names of his
OL,12,Fwife and mother-in-law, as well as an
OL,13,F"extensive review" of his published
OL,14,Fwork.
OL,16,FMr Bunting said Mr Kearney should
OL,17,Freceive "substantial" damages.
OL,19,FCathryn McGahey KC, for the PSNI, said
OL,20,Fthe force had made "a number of clear
OL,21,Fand extensive concessions".
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@fO]uD@AOUuD@RO]yD@IOUyD@UO]|D@
