PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784922490
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist whose data was
OL,4,Cunlawfully gained awarded #20,000 in
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FThe barrister said in written
OL,8,Fsubmissions that "the interferences in
OL,9,Fquestion were directed at the
OL,10,Facquisition of communications data
OL,11,Fassociated with an individual
OL,12,Fjournalist, rather than at the BBC's
OL,13,Feditorial autonomy, premises, systems,
OL,14,For journalistic archives".
OL,26,@pD@ROUvD@YO]
