PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784922490
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist whose data was
OL,4,Cunlawfully gained awarded #20,000 in
OL,5,Cdamages
OL,7,FMs McGahey continued that while the
OL,8,Fforce did not object to the tribunal
OL,9,Fruling that the PSNI breached Mr
OL,10,FKearney and the BBC's rights, it
OL,11,Fopposed the journalist being awarded
OL,12,Fdamages as it would be unnecessary "to
OL,13,Faward just satisfaction".
